    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-technology\">significant</span> upgrade for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Mining Beam</span>.<br><br>Upgrades the Mining Laser's primary crystal chamber, boosting core <span class=\"name name-stellar\">beam energy</span> while decreasing unwanted <span class=\"name name-stellar\">heat spill</span>.",
